{"type": "article", "id": 19939, "title": "Union 扑克牌", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-30T07:20:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607103927LxoTgeMWI0lwqsJk.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t美国平面设计师 Jay Fletcher 设计了这幅扑克牌包装和它的展示架。深棕色的扑克牌近似一块黑巧克力或者一盒香烟，适合一个有酒的夜晚。扑克牌里面将美国元素巧妙设计成图案，很有纪念意义。展示架的木头来自查尔斯敦海军船坞，有 300 年历史，上面有四个凹槽卡住扑克牌，显得原始而硬朗。售价 9.95 美元，<a href=\"http://store.theory11.com/products/union-playing-cards#order-now\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150308R6X8JiVBf20Ipx5d.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"402\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7472119\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261503098HLOQyuBajTtIq6V.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"359\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66728625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150309dq0UhGzE9aH8lsyg.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"424\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.78810409\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150310G7bHFsULt0BaP8xf.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"458\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.85130112\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072615031025sacZxprTJPqDuo.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"804\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}